data.description: This 4 bed 3 full bath home is ready for its new owners! Come and check out this conveniently located and wonderfully kept home that is fully equipped with all stainless steel kitchen appliances, washer and dryer, and a water softener. This versatile floor plan provides ample space for everyone in your home. As you walk in through the front door you will find a bedroom with a full bathroom near the front laundry area. Further past the entrance you are greeted with natural light beaming in the main open living space. The kitchen over looks the dining an living area, which is perfect for entertaining. Upstairs are the remaining 2 bedrooms, the primary suite, and a spacious loft area. Don't miss your opportunity to make this home yours!
